Primary scenario (call center)
- Agent receives phone call
- Agent subscribes to TranscriptReceived events
- Saga coordinates deterministic flow
- State written to Redis
- Transcripts sent to LLM suggestions pipeline
- Pipeline raises SuggestionsGenerated events
- Suggestions streamed to frontend

Key value points to emphasize
- Telemetry is easier with events
- Event sourcing and replayability: filter by event type
- Flexibility of async, decoupled flows

Downfalls to emphasize
- Complexity grows quickly even in small repo
- Naming pitfalls: <EventNameConsumer> vs <ResultingEvent>
- Observability and ordering pitfalls
- Event schema versioning pressure

